{
  "chapter": 50,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤与独孤美在黑暗中逃亡，依靠磷光指引穿越吃人树林。途中独孤美被毒蛇咬伤，陆小凤为他吸出毒液，这份义举打动了原本不打算带他去山庄的独孤美。天亮后二人脱困，在古松下发现幽灵山庄留下的补给箱，内含食物、药品和一只联络哨子。独孤美揭示山庄名为\"幽灵山庄\"，是一个只有死人才能去的秘密之地。二人循哨声进入万丈深渊，遇到幽灵山庄的勾魂使者——一个脸被削平、没有嘴唇、轻功惊人的神秘人物。勾魂使者拒绝接纳没有合约的陆小凤，但老刀把子下令将二人全部带入。陆小凤拒绝坐竹篮，选择走横跨深渊的钢索，途中被勾魂使者用乌木簪偷袭坠落，却以超凡轻功脚钩钢索化险为夷。勾魂使者承认自己的剑比西门吹雪更快，随后消失。陆小凤最终越过生死线，踏入幽灵山庄的死人世界。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "顺着这磷光走，就能走出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我绝对有把握。因为你只要跟他们有了合约，他们就绝不会出卖你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "他们是谁？是不是山庄里的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "什么山庄？在哪里？你跟他们订的是什么合约？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妹妹背着泥娃娃，走到花园来看花。娃娃哭了叫妈妈，树上的小鸟笑哈哈……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "蛇……毒蛇！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你怎么知道是毒蛇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我被它咬到的地方，一点都不疼，只发麻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "伤口在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就在我左肩上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你已觉得痛了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你若还能睡，就睡一下，睡不着就捱一会儿，反正天已快亮了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你本来不必这么做的！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你既然已知道出路，为什么还不抛下我一个人走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "也许只因为你还会笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "我总觉得，一个人只要还会笑，就不能算是六亲不认的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "前面是不是有棵大松树？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "松树下是不是有块大石块？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "我们总算出来了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只可惜这里还不能算是安全的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "我总算还没有被那吃人的树林子吃下去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只可惜你还是随时都可能死在西门吹雪剑下！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你能不能说两句让人听了比较高兴的话？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只不过想告诉你一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这世上本来已没有人能救得了你，但你却自己救了自己。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你刚才救我的时候，也同时救了你自己。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你本来并不是真的想带我到那山庄中去的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是，我现在已改变了主意，因为我就算是个六亲不认的人，总算还是个人。你在那种情况下都没有甩下我，现在我当然也不能甩下你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "去搬开那块石头看看，下面是不是有口箱子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "好酒。看来这些人想得实在周到。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他们做事不但计划周密，而且信誉卓着，你只要跟他们有了合约，他们就一定会负责送你到山庄去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "什么合约？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "救命的合约。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "什么山庄？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "幽灵山庄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "难道那地方全是死人的幽灵？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就因为那地方全都是死人的幽灵，所以没有一个活人能找得到，更没有一个活人敢闯进去！",
      "tone": "神秘",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我既然已走了死路，当然非死不可。",
      "tone": "神秘",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你既然已非死不可，当然就已是个死人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你总算明白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "我不明白，一点也不明白。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你再吹一声哨子试试看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "要到幽灵山庄去，看来也并不是什么困难的事，你只要往下面一跳，保证立刻就会变成个死人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你就是幽灵山庄的勾魂使者？我叫独孤美，我的魂已来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "我知道，我知道你会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你不敢看我？是不是因为我太丑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我不是……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "既然不是，就看着我说话，看着我的脸。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你本该一个人来的，现在为什么有两个？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你留下，他走！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "他也不走。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "他不走，你走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我有合约，是你们自己订的合约。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你有，他没有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "他是我的朋友，他的合约金我可以替他付。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "现在就付？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "随时都可以付，我身上带着有……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "就算现在付，也已太迟了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "因为我说的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "可是他既然已来到这里，就绝不能再活着回去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你若想救他，你就自己走，留下他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你留下，我走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "你用不着担心我，我既然能活着来到这里，就一定有法子活着回去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你没有把死活放在心上，我却很怕死……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "可是你现在已经不怕了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "因为你反正也活不长的，不如把机会让给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这是惟一的机会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "这些话我早就听你说过，你的意思我也很明白，只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你还是不肯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "能够跟一个六亲不认的人交上朋友，我已经很满意了，只可惜我一向没有要朋友替我死的习惯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "独孤美",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你一定要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_mei",
      "text": "我走得一定比你快。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_hong_se_ren_ying",
      "speaker_name": "淡红色人影",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "带他们进来，两个人全都带进来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_ying_hong_se_ren_ying",
      "text": "谁说要将他们全都带进去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_hong_se_ren_ying",
      "speaker_name": "淡红色人影",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "老刀把子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是不是也想坐进去？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我有腿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "若是一跤跌下去，就没有腿了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "非但没有腿，连尸骨都没有，一跌下去，人就变成了肉酱。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我想得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这条钢索很滑，山里的风很大，无论轻功多么好的人，走在上面，随时都可能会跌下去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你跌下去过？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你喜欢我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "既然你没有跌下去过，又怎么知道我会跌下去？既然你并不喜欢我，又何必关心我的死活？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，你先走。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你要在后面等着看我跌下去？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这种机会很多，我一向不愿错过。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "可是这一次我保证你一定会失望的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我唱的歌好不好听？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那不是唱歌，是驴子叫。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "原来你也有受不了的时候，好，好，好极了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是陆小凤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "怎么我一唱歌你就认出我来了？难道我的歌声比我的人还要出名？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你真的是陆小凤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "除了陆小凤外，还有谁能唱这样的歌？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "这世上不要脸的人虽多，却还没有一个做得像你这么彻底的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "看来你真的是陆小凤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "现在虽然还是陆小凤，等一下说不定就会变成一堆肉酱了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你真的不怕死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "看来你好像也不是真的要我死。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只不过想要你知道一件事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我要你知道，西门吹雪并不是天下无双的快剑，我比他更快。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_hun_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "勾魂使者",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是个不要脸的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "冲过这条生死线，你已是个死人。所以你最好再想一想，是走过来，还是回头去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你，饶了我吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 650
    }
  ],
